1
00:00:58,840 --> 00:01:01,280
The Resentment Transfer Ritual is an ancient secret art

2
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:03,880
It can deceive a Vengeful Spirit consumed by resentment

3
00:01:04,520 --> 00:01:06,520
This art uses the scent of the deceased's belongings

4
00:01:06,760 --> 00:01:08,480
to lure the Vengeful Spirit into a paper figurine

5
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:10,080
When the day of Bone-gathering comes

6
00:01:10,360 --> 00:01:12,040
the paper figurine is burned along with it

7
00:01:12,520 --> 00:01:14,000
and the resentment can be dispelled

8
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:16,680
Clear heavens

9
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:18,240
bright sun and moon

10
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,480
Resentment, begone

11
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:22,160
Return to the body

12
00:01:26,040 --> 00:01:26,680
Look

13
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:35,240
Master Wang

14
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:38,200
Not a single thing in this room can be touched

15
00:01:38,360 --> 00:01:39,760
until the paper figurine speaks

16
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:41,120
A paper figurine

17
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:45,120
A paper figurine can talk?

18
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:46,520
That's right

19
00:01:47,240 --> 00:01:51,400
But since the ritual is already done

20
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:55,800
why don't we have tea in the front hall?

21
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,840
Master

22
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,920
Look at you, look at you

23
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:06,680
Just leave these things to the servants

24
00:02:06,880 --> 00:02:08,920
Why trouble yourself with them?

25
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:10,920
Master, the tonic soup is ready

26
00:02:10,920 --> 00:02:11,880
Please drink it while it's hot

27
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,080
Sit, sit, sit

28
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:16,640
What am I supposed to do with you?

29
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:24,360
Fifth Concubine, you are fragrant all over

30
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:35,960
Mr. Zheng, please forgive the embarrassment

31
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:41,880
I wonder if you have a wife and children

32
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:45,280
I'm just a lowly bone-gatherer

33
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:47,360
How could I have Master Wang's good fortune?

34
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:50,560
to marry a beauty like the Fifth Concubine

35
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:54,200
Yes, yes

36
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:55,960
But, Mr. Zheng

37
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:59,720
For a man, as long as he saves enough money

38
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:03,120
tell me, what kind of pretty woman

39
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,800
could we not marry in the future?

40
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:07,520
Isn't that right, Fifth Concubine?

41
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:11,480
Just look at our Fifth Concubine

42
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:13,080
That waist

43
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:16,240
That skin, so fair

44
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:20,520
Those little hands, so soft

45
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:29,760
I won't disturb Master Wang and his concubine

46
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,040
What did you come to the Wang house for?

47
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:51,600
Do you know

48
00:03:51,760 --> 00:03:53,680
Wang Shengchang's spies are everywhere here

49
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:01,760
You're worried I'll be in danger?

50
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:05,240
Fifth Concubine, you really are affectionate

51
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:08,080
You were just acting all sweet with Master Wang

52
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:10,640
and now you come worry about a lowly bone-gatherer

53
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:14,080
Aren't you afraid your master will find out?

54
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:25,200
At a time like this, and you're still joking?

55
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:27,400
What exactly did you come to the Wang house for?

56
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:34,520
Don't you know why I came?

57
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:37,240
Doesn't the Fifth Concubine want to know

58
00:04:37,280 --> 00:04:39,760
how the Wang family's former concubines died?

59
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:42,320
The Wang family is hiding quite a few secrets

60
00:04:45,320 --> 00:04:48,960
My master's death is tied to the Wang family too

61
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,600
If you want to know the truth

62
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:53,240
come find me tonight

63
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:57,480
I will show you whether Wang Shengchang is man or ghost

64
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:08,600
When did the bright moon first appear?

65
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:11,600
With wine in hand, I ask the blue heavens

66
00:05:16,440 --> 00:05:18,600
Why won't you help me take revenge?

67
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:21,600
You knew perfectly well it was the Wang family

68
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,400
I'm sorry

69
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,480
I failed to protect you

70
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:33,120
My right hand still hasn't been found

71
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:35,760
I died so unjustly

72
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:39,080
Shuang'er, I will kill Wang Shengchang

73
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:40,760
and avenge you

74
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:42,640
Then do it

75
00:05:43,400 --> 00:05:47,080
Just in time, that old man is here

76
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,040
Help!

77
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:51,520
Help!

78
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,080
Help!

79
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:55,880
Wang Shengchang, where are you?

80
00:05:56,960 --> 00:05:58,160
Don't run, Wang Shengchang

81
00:05:58,280 --> 00:05:59,440
Give me back my right hand

82
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:03,600
Wang Shengchang, don't run

83
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,240
I found you

84
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:11,560
I'm here

85
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:14,480
Spare me, spare me

86
00:06:14,840 --> 00:06:16,880
You are the one who got me killed

87
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:19,280
Today I will make you pay with your life

88
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:21,080
No, it wasn't me

89
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,360
It wasn't me

90
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:24,920
Shuang'er died so horribly

91
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:27,200
Today someone must pay with a life

92
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:28,720
No, no, it wasn't

93
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:31,440
It was Madam, it was Madam

94
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:32,960
Don't blame me

95
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:35,040
Madam Wang is the one who killed Miss Shuang'er

96
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:38,600
Spare me, it wasn't me

97
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:40,000
Speak

98
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:42,400
How many people have you killed?

99
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:55,800
Run

100
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:13,280
That thing is not human

101
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:16,880
Go

102
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:32,520
Run forward, don't look back
